  </div>
  <p class="subtitle" id="animated-subtitle">MINDCUBE Benchmark for Spatial Reasoning in VLMs</p>
  <p class="description">
    <b>TL;DR:</b> Current Vision-Language Models (VLMs) can't build mental models of space from limited viewpoints like humans can. We introduce the MINDCUBE benchmark and show that teaching VLMs to generate their own cognitive maps and reason over them dramatically improves spatial understandingâ€”boosting performance from 38% to 76% (+37.8%).
  </p>
  <div class="resources-section">
    <div class="resources-buttons">
      <a href="#" class="resource-button"><span>Paper</span></a>
